{"tid":1144254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《逃犯條例》修訂一旦通過，有機會違反《香港政策法》多項關鍵條款","createTime":"2019-05-08T03:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T07:10:09.000Z","uid":5195,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"fdac4b4b0d21278f6a4cb1e05efc36e7d5a10062","tid":1144254,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:40:17.000Z","msg":"美國國會的諮詢機構美中經濟與安全審查委員會（USCC）指，《逃犯條例》修訂一旦通過，有機會違反《美國-香港政策法》的多項關鍵條款，包括美港兩地的引渡條約，亦影響美國企業繼續在香港經營的意欲，直言條例通過的話，勢將「削弱與損害香港作為美國與國際企業安全營商地點的聲譽」。"},{"pid":"9509ccaa90e15557e4775658e7155a72e8191fbb","tid":1144254,"uid":170044,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:41:40.000Z","msg":"玩焦土"},{"pid":"291bfb25d202423a2fce53add94d5a1707dd1511","tid":1144254,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":35,"score":-34,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8a5049f70fe4d7b2ea683d3148b9fe69e835a63","tid":1144254,"uid":143241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:46:13.000Z","msg":"柒婆:我就係想咁,你吹咩"},{"pid":"4ef0293f1dc31f7749a5cc3a55f555e2be1dd81c","tid":1144254,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76712b4f70ec18e029c1832a3611bfb08f50d1d5","tid":1144254,"uid":198616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:49:22.000Z","msg":"大劉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e660df3430825d57dc69b5b60cd632fdbb6694","tid":1144254,"uid":221171,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"291bfb25d202423a2fce53add94d5a1707dd1511","tid":1144254,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":35,"score":-34,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CxKjU6p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxKjU6p.png&h=a8c07983&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d883979d54620153352257885ce6febb0f481fd","tid":1144254,"uid":113373,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰<br />\n<br />\n星期六 早上8點半 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n為下一代想想<br />\n此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d42f2a4cf28e50074f981d018e5d8b26ddef2de8","tid":1144254,"uid":206522,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:52:51.000Z","msg":"係取消就襯早啦<br />\n講幾十次都唔取消"},{"pid":"8908f2c8733995fe3926863bb8fb775fe905b527","tid":1144254,"uid":160051,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"侵幾時發個Twitter講下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5335832a2146624369095bcc5674d612049a9e72","tid":1144254,"uid":36390,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"香港不需要香港關係法，一國兩制保民護國，全宇宙最厲害"},{"pid":"6004b32a0cccbf6fa9212b0f16743ef1923062e0","tid":1144254,"uid":20689,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"291bfb25d202423a2fce53add94d5a1707dd1511","tid":1144254,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":35,"score":-34,"citedBy":12,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:59:01.000Z","msg":"無所審判 即時列入五毛條列 bye!"},{"pid":"6aca22df81764dea369b4b2476f08f2e0c4fe673","tid":1144254,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cb4322fbb2db19a52468e84ffd944d89eb910d","tid":1144254,"uid":122377,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T05:21:25.000Z","msg